Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I swear that we will come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then let's go on adventures\Ntogether all across the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! We'll now go into the\NGrand Line and travel around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wait for us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bink's Booze! The Song that\NConnects the Past with the Present!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Your quick draw is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to fight with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waterspouts?! But we had\Nclear skies a second ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Common sense is meaningless on these waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, there is no telling what\Nthis ocean will throw at us next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that is what makes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the booze at the end of \Nthe day taste so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please play that song for us again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting you to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I'm a skeleton now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! That really hurts, Captain!\NWhy are you hanging me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! You've got nerve to\Nfight over something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, his stray bullet\Nnearly got me killed in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, aren't you?!\NBesides, he offered you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't nag over the past! It's unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pain is proof you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clear, starry night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Laboon is\Nlooking up at these stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Check this out! Brook is\Ngetting mushy on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kn-Knock that off! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Navy Headquarters!\NWhat should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go chicken on me! Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's bounty went up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I great?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorkie! Yorkie! Let your infamy\Nresound clear to the Twin Cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the captain...! Something is\Nwrong with Captain Yorkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:07:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plague?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few dozen crew members have been infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may have contracted it\Nin that jungle we just visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unknown virus. I can't treat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make one false move,\Neveryone onboard might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sound so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll mar the name of the Rumbar Pirates\Nthat make crying children laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am pulling out of the Grand Line\Na little ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take this worn-out ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that it has become \Na carrier for the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Push forward on a new ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed I would drop out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take our chances... and try\Nto escape through the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everything will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Laboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe those sniveling expressions off\Nyour faces! Get your acts together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good for you \Nguys to hang out in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going! Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorkie is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along. Let's head on out, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filled with regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorkie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget those words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have chiseled them into my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to travel on separate ships now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's survive so we \Ncan see everyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take off that mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sing with everyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please see me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with that song I love so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail leisurely with the sea breeze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail with the waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The setting sun romps about\Non the other side of the tide... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:55.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"10 Years After Leaving Twin Cape\N-Florian Triangle-"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took off my pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear! That was so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so fun! Even when\NI'm alone, I can have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,45 degree angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Someone, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I'm all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Are you gonna sleep forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! We spotted an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summer island! It has a beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Ah, uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping you, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get started without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? How come you are alive? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NIsn't it time you woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that to have hurt, it means\Nthis isn't a dream. It's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all a dream! Thank goo--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Captain Yorkie made it\Nthrough the Calm Belt in one piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean is a mysterious place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's carry on his will and plow forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will head toward Laboon on this new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up! I'm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nasty storm!\NThe sails are gonna get torn to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing! Let's \Nsing our way through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, Brook has\Ngotten a bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why'd you stop?\NKeep the music going, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him! I was dancing\Nwith chopsticks up my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Awesome!\N--That's how your head works?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I bought this from a\Nmerchant ship. It's called a "Tone Dial."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unusual shell that records sounds\Nand allows you to play them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's from the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see Laboon, I want \Nhim to listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep it close to my heart at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm a skeleton, \NI don't have a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you recorded something onto it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains my crewmates singing\Nwhen they were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our message to Laboon: \NWe were happy and cheerful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we finished our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I play it for you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanna hear it! I bet Laboon'll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without further ado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people... are still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be alive, but it doesn't\Nlook like we'll pull through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it means to get wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They laced their weapons with poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've lost the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate. I've always \Nbeen prepared to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My one regret is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, does your Revive-Revive Fruit work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. I've never died before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. If we're going to die anyway,\Nlet's enjoy the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the power of the Revive-Revive Fruit\Ntruly does bring me back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take this to Laboon! I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Tone Dial...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will record the song that Laboon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe captain, and all of us loved so dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon is waiting at that cape under
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the belief that we'll return \Ntoday or tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Guys, don't keel over\Nbefore the song is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Rumbar Pirate's\Nchoral number of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can sing along with this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bink's Booze"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail leisurely with the sea breeze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail with the waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The setting sun romps about\Non the other side of the tide ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A ring of birds in the sky sing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Bid farewell to the port\Nof the weaving village ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ As we set sail, we \Nshall sing heartily ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Silver and gold waves \Nturn into ocean spray ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We are off, bound for\Nthe ends of the ocean ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We are pirates, sailing \Nacross the seas ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The waves are my pillow,\Nthe ship my lodge ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A skull flies proud \Non our sails and flags ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A storm has hit a distant village ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The waves are dancing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sound the drums ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ If the cowardly wind blows, that's it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There won't be a sunrise \Ntomorrow morning ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Either today or tomorrow,\NI'll be lost in a dream ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Never again will I meet... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...the hand that waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ But why brood over it? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There will be another\Nmoonlit night tomorrow ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ As we sail on the seas,\Nwe shall sing heartily ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Everyone turns into \Nbones someday anyway ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Life is a silly story\Nwithout an ending or direction ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?\NThis has turned into a quartet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A solo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Why is the\Naccompaniment the last to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to join my crew,\Nyou must have a love of music!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the sail of the Rumbar Pirates\Nthat make crying children laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, I swear that we will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be here waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, if you have been waiting\Nthere for the past fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...could you give me just \Nanother year or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take pride in being a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are facing the wall, I want to greet\Nyou from the front, just like I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the dead and skeletonized Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a wanted man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bounty for 33 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, my life belongs to you,\NCaptain Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A New Crewmate!\NThe Musician, Humming Brook!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
